text: Jeannette Goergen-Philipp (born 30 November 1947) is a Luxembourgian archer. Goergen-Philipp competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and at the 1992 Summer Olympics.Jeannette Goergen-PhilipJeannette PHILIPP-GOERGEN == References == Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Luxembourgian archers Category:Olympians for Luxembourg
